  "title": "Stage compere",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities</p>\n<p>• Attend auditions or castings for a role in a play or performance.</p>\n<p>• Deliver performance smoothly and perfectly.</p>\n<p>• Rehearse with other actors and the producer to familiarise themselves with the act.</p>\n<p>• Understand the storyline and role of production from the producer and scriptwriter.</p>\n<p>• Work on comments and feedback given by the director, producer, and other actors.</p>\n<p>• Adhoc job is given by manager</p>\n<p>• Working hours are from 9pm to 5am</p>\n<p>Requirements and skills</p>\n<p>• Ability to work under pressure</p>\n<p>• High standard of organizational and communication skills</p>\n<p>• Problem-solving skills, ability to think on your feet</p>\n<p><br></p>",
